{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1686-11a_086", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Question galante avec la réponse]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", novembre 1686 (première partie) [tome 15], p. 86-88"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les belles Personnes ont un privilege particulier pour estre de cette galante Cour, mais elles y font rarement fracas si leur beauté n’est accompagnée des agrémens de l’esprit. Ainsi je ne doute point que vous ne soyez du sentiment de celuy qui a décidé une Question que vous aurez sans doute oüy souvent proposer, & qui a esté faite encore depuis peu dans les termes que je vous l’envoye."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Demande."}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Si vous aviez dessein d’aimer,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui pourroit plûtost vous charmer,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Ou la Sotte qui seroit belle,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Ou la Laide spirituelle ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Response."}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " La Bestise est un Monstre affreux"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Qui fait tout paroistre hideux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce qu’on en voit atteint n’a rien qui ne déplaise,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Et je dis hardiment de bouche & par écrit,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Qu’un laid Objet remply d’esprit"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Me charmeroit plûtost qu’une Beauté niaise."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}